    <div class="container">
        <h1>Worker Guidelines</h1>
        <p>Follow these guidelines to ensure a smooth and professional experience for both you and the customer.</p>

        <h2>Code of Conduct</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Be punctual and professional</li>
            <li>Communicate clearly with customers</li>
            <li>Provide quality service and maintain high standards</li>
            <li>Follow safety and hygiene protocols</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Service Policies</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Accept job requests promptly</li>
            <li>Confirm appointments with customers</li>
            <li>In case of cancellation, inform customers in advance</li>
            <li>Report any issues to customer support</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Following these guidelines will help you build a great reputation and earn more jobs!</strong></p>
